    "html_format": "<div class=\"document-view-wrapper\">\n<style>\n.html-preview * {font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview a.NoteRef {text-decoration: none;}\n.html-preview table td {vertical-align: top;}\n.html-preview table {width: 100%;}\n.html-preview p {white-space: pre-wrap;}\n.html-preview .leading {width: 4px; display: inline-block;}\n.html-preview hr {height: 1px; padding: 0; margin: 1em 0; border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #CCC;}\n.html-preview .Normal {className: Normal; margin-bottom: 10pt;}\n.html-preview .a3 {font-family: 'Calibri';}\n.html-preview .a4 {font-family: 'Calibri';}\n.html-preview .a5 {font-family: 'Calibri';}\n</style>\n<div class=\"html-preview\">\n<style>.html-preview{width: 762px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-top: 76px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-bottom: 32px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-left: 81px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-right: 57px}</style><table>\n<tr>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\" width: 311.86703601108px;\">\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span></p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\" width: 324.43213296399px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">Иқтисодий ишлар бўйича </span><span class=\"structures structure-3\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">{#3}Ариза берилган иқтисодий суди номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\"> судига</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#6}Ариза берувчининг манзили</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"structures structure-7\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#7}Ариза берувчи юридик шахс номи ёки якка тартибдаги тадбиркор (ЯТТ)нинг Ф.И.Оси</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">дан</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td 1=\"\" style=\" width: 324.43213296399px;\">\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td 2=\"\" style=\" width: 324.43213296399px;\">\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: center; margin-top: 2pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">А<span class=\"leading\"></span>Р И З А</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">(прокурорни рад этиш тўғрисида)</span></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: center; margin-top: 2pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 60px;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 47.2px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Бераман ушбу аризани шу ҳақдаким, даъвогар </span><span class=\"structures structure-10\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#10}Иш бўйича даъвогар ташкилотнинг ташкилий ҳуқуқий шакли ва номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">нинг жавобгар </span><span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#11}Иш бўйича жавобгар ташкилотнинг ташкилий ҳуқуқий шакли ва номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">га нисбатан <span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-12\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#12}Даъво ариза мазмуни</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> ҳақидаги даъво аризаси юзасидан иқтисодий ишда прокурор сифатида иштирок этаётган </span><span class=\"structures structure-13\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#13}Суд жараёнида иштирок этаётган прокурорнинг Ф.И.О.си</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">га нисбатан раддия бераман. Чунки прокурор </span><span class=\"structures structure-14\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#14}Прокурорга раддия бериш сабаблари</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> ҳисобланади.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 47.2px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Ўзбекистон Республикаси ИПКнинг 21-моддасига кўра, прокурор ишда иштирок этувчи шахсларнинг ёки улар вакилларининг қариндоши бўлса, ишнинг натижасидан шахсан, бевосита ёки билвосита манфаатдор бўлса ёхуд унинг холислигига шубҳа туғдирувчи бошқа ҳолатлар мавжуд бўлса ишни кўришда иштирок этиши мумкин эмас ва рад қилиниши лозим. </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 47.2px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Шу сабабли Ўзбекистон Республикаси ИПКнинг 21, 22-моддаларига асосан <span class=\"leading\"></span>бошқа прокурор иштирокини таъминлашингизни сўрайман.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 47.266666666667px;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 47.266666666667px;\"></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\" width: 212.07756232687px;\">\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-top: 2pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span class=\"structures structure-8\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#8}Ариза берувчи юридик шахс раҳбарининг ёки якка тартибдаги тадбиркор (ЯТТ)нинг Ф.И.Оси</span></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-top: 2pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\" width: 212.07756232687px;\">\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" margin-top: 2pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: center; margin-top: 2pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">имзо</span></p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\" width: 212.14404432133px;\">\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: right; margin-top: 2pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span class=\"structures structure-4\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#4}Ариза берилган сана</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p style=\"